name: service-catalog-management
description: ## TMF API Reference: TMF633 - Service Catalog Management   Version 4.0   The Service Catalog API is one of Catalog Management API Family. Service Catalog API goal is to provide a catalog of services.  Service Catalog API performs the following operations on the resource : - Retrieve an entity or a collection of entities depending on filter criteria - Partial update of an entity (including updating rules) - Create an entity (including default values and creation rules) - Delete an entity (for administration purposes) - Manage notification of events. .
